{"type":"text","timestamp":1778635160558,"sessionID":"ses_1e1157f78ffe8Ay8SmEz377dxA","part":{"id":"prt_e1eeab2aa001KX9x5mqDOuaCn6","messageID":"msg_e1eea9e9b001S7AsiQkU2GsWxl","sessionID":"ses_1e1157f78ffe8Ay8SmEz377dxA","type":"text","text":"The prior `micro_opt` history rules out front-end state, forwarding recoding, reg-file reshaping, MEM lane rewrites, broad ALU sharing, and syntax-only cleanup. The narrowest remaining promising angle is a timing-only decode/control simplification that removes unused control bits from hot stage payloads without altering pipeline behavior.","time":{"start":1778635158186,"end":1778635160557},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_08a8d31a7c8d1678016a03d1961818819b859913753ff7703d","phase":"commentary"}}}}
