part\":{\"id\":\"prt_e1eeb6f1d001ps1y4bpJ9agew5\",\"messageID\":\"msg_e1eeb6aca001dcB7evD3xSxlB6\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_1e11580c0ffeSwchj8aKCTzhE6\",\"snapshot\":\"7a5bb6c63748311e5ebc6d96393a7c81253dd773\",\"type\":\"step-start\"}}\n\n(End of file - total 16 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"{\"type\":\"step_start\",\"timestamp\":1778635147079,\"sessionID\":\"ses_1e11580c0ffeSwchj8aKCTzhE6\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_e1eea8746001Of2cLs1bJJeZiI\",\"messageID\":\"msg_e1eea7fa90011746LT4NWoQX5Y\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_1e11580c0ffeSwchj8aKCTzhE6\",\"snapshot\":\"7a5bb6c63748311e5ebc6d96393a7c81253dd773\",\"type\":\"step-start\"}}\n{\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1778635161672,\"sessionID\":\"ses_1e11580c0ffeSwchj8aKCTzhE6\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_e1eeab19a001MSq1RNkioh2LOq\",\"messageID\":\"msg_e1eea7fa90011746LT4NWoQX5Y\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_1e11580c0ffeSwchj8aKCTzhE6\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"I’ll inspect the bench lessons/log for prior predictor attempts, then write the requested hypothesis file only under `cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/`.\",\"time\":{\"start\":1778635157914,\"end\":1778635161671},\"metadata\":{\"openai\":{\"itemId\":\"msg_0dcbe94daa0701a1016a03d195d0988198aaf6aeda51f7787c\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}}}}\n{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1778635161699,\"sessionID\":\"ses_1e11580c0ffeSwchj8aKCTzhE6\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_4OWRV3zDxLzXJtC5cEp6TJET\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/Users/bonetto/bonetto/auto-arch-tournament/.claude/bench-runs/gpt-5_5_high-rep1/cores/bench/LESSONS.md\",\"offset\":1,\"limit\":240},\"output\":\"<path>/Users/bonetto/bonetto/auto-arch-tournament/.claude/bench-runs/gpt-5_5_high-rep1/cores/bench/LESSONS.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: - 2026-05-12 hyp-20260512-001-r1s0 (regression, +4.17%): Decode-to-IF JAL fast paths can lose more to added imem/decode/PC-mux timing than they save in bubbles, so direct jumps are better handled by a lightweight fetch predictor or kept off the critical PC path.\\n2: - 2026-05-12 hyp-20260512-002-r1s1 (regression, +3.34%): A sequential IF FIFO that only buffers pc+4 fetches did not hide enough randomized imem/dmem backpressure to pay for its extra queue/control state, so front-end decoupling needs redirect-aware prefetch value beyond isolated stall absorption.\\n3: - 2026-05-12 hyp-20260512-003-r1s2 (improvement, +19.74%): Static fetch prediction for JAL and backward BRANCH targets pays on CoreMark's tight counted loops because carrying pred_next_pc to EX removes taken-back-edge redirect bubbles without BTB state or broadening the critical path much.\\n4: - 2026-05-12 hyp-20260512-001-r2s0 (broken, n/a): Load-to-store stalls can only be pruned if the MEM-stage store-data bypass also updates RVFI rs2 source metadata; fixing dmem_wdata alone leaves stale ID-read operands that riscv-formal's reg check catches.\\n5: - 2026-05-12 hyp-20260512-002-r2s1 (regression, -10.26%): A one-entry store buffer that still stalls all younger loads/stores behind sb_valid adds dmem mux/control cost without enough CoreMark memory-level parallelism to offset it; store decoupling needs forwarding or deeper disambiguation to pay.\\n6: - 2026-05-12 hyp-20260512-003-r2s2 (regression, -1.79%): A tiny... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1778635161868,\"sessionID\":\"ses_1e11580c0ffeSwchj8aKCTzhE6\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"glob\",\"callID\":\"call_V99jxXQcLLal5DxzdCKo4puE\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"pattern\":\"cores/bench/experiments/hypotheses/*.yaml\",\"path\":\"/Users/bonetto/bonetto/auto-arch-tournament/.claude/bench-runs/gpt-5_5_high-rep1\"},\"output\":\"No files found\",\"metadata\":{\"count\":0,\"truncated\":false},\"title\":\"\",\"time\":{\"start\":1778635161851,\"end\":1778635161867}},\"metadata\":{\"openai\":{\"itemId\":\"fc_0dcbe94daa0701a1016a03d19990b08198adabf4c524b3f098\"}},\"id\":\"prt_e1eeac0fa001a9D46TocfAPPgb\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_1e11580c0ffeSwchj8aKCTzhE6\",\"messageID\":\"msg_e1eea7fa90011746LT4NWoQX5Y\"}}\n{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1778635161869,\"sessionID\":\"ses_1e11580c0ffeSwchj8aKCTzhE6\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"grep\",\"callID\":\"call_ofC5cx9VzuGDteueoL6R0Wm0\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"pattern\":\"predict|BHT|BTB|RAS|JALR|branch|loop|fallthrough|pred_next_pc|fetch\",\"path\":\"/Users/bonetto/bonetto/auto-arch-tournament/.claude/bench-runs/gpt-5_5_high-rep1/cores/bench/experiments\",\"include\":\"log.jsonl\"},\"output\":\"Found 40 matches\\n/Users/bonetto/bonetto/auto-arch-tournament/.claude/bench-runs/gpt-5_5_high-rep1/cores/bench/experiments/log.jsonl:\\n  Line 2: {\\\"id\\\": \\\"hyp-20260512-001-r1s0\\\", \\\"title\\\": \\\"Resolve JAL one stage earlier\\\", \\\"category\\\": \\\"micro_opt\\\", \\\"motivation\\\": \\\"CoreMark contains frequent unconditional calls and loop-control jumps. The current\\\\npipeline treats JAL like every other control transfer and redirects from EX, so each\\\\ntaken JAL pays the same two wrong-path bubbles as a conditional branch even though\\\\nits target is fully known from the instruction bits in decode.\\\\n\\\", \\\"hypothesis\\\": {\\\"motivation\\\": \\\"CoreMark contains frequent unconditional calls and loop-control jumps. The current\\\\npipeline treats JAL like every other control transfer and redirects from EX, so each\\\\ntaken JAL pays the same two wrong-path bubbles as a conditional branch even though\\\\nits target is fully known from the instruction bits in decode.\\\\n\\\", \\\"hypothesis\\\": \\\"Add a decode/IF fast path for legal JAL instructions: compute the J-immediate target\\\\nfrom the IF/ID instruction and redirect the PC before the instruction reaches EX,\\\\nwhile preserving the normal EX-stage JAL result and RVFI pc_wdata bookkeeping for\\\\nretirement. JALR and conditional branches remain EX-resolved because they require\\\\nregister operands or comparison results. This should reduce CoreMark cycles by\\\\nremoving one redirect bubble from unconditional direct jumps with minimal timing cost.\\\\n\\\", \\\"expected_impact\\\": {\\\"fitness_delta_pct\\\": 3, \\\"confidence\\\": \\\"medium\\\"}... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n{\"type\":\"step_finish\",\"timestamp\":1778635162090,\"sessionID\":\"ses_1e11580c0ffeSwchj8aKCTzhE6\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_e1eeac1e9001k5kQO0wzO0sAhv\",\"reason\":\"tool-calls\",\"snapshot\":\"7a5bb6c63748311e5ebc6d96393a7c81253dd773\",\"messageID\":\"msg_e1eea7fa90011746LT4NWoQX5Y\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_1e11580c0ffeSwchj8aKCTzhE6\",\"type\":\"step-finish\",\"tokens\":{\"total\":41456,\"input\":25314,\"output\":266,\"reasoning\":516,\"cache\":{\"write\":0,\"read\":15360}},\"cost\":0}}\n{\"type\":\"step_start\",\"timestamp\":1778635163267,\"sessionID\":\"ses_1e11580c0ffeSwchj8aKCTzhE6\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_e1eeac6820011aHnZZRlgBP4ej\",\"messageID\":\"msg_e1eeac20a001VpTmyrduiUKdTe\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_1e11580c0ffeSwchj8aKCTzhE6\",\"snapshot\":\"7a5bb6c63748311e5ebc6d96393a7c81253dd773\",\"type\":\"step-start\"}}\n{\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1778635172654,\"sessionID\":\"ses_1e11580c0ffeSwchj8aKCTzhE6\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_e1eeada75001S3N9sk3H4onUiK\",\"messageID\":\"msg_e1eeac20a001VpTmyrduiUKdTe\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_1e11580c0ffeSwchj8aKCTzhE6\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The prior predictor history strongly favors preserving the existing JAL/backward-branch policy and avoiding new IF-stage state. I’m going to frame this hypothesis as a very narrow predictor implementation-cost reduction, not a smarter predictor.\",\"time\":{\"start\":1778635168373,\"end\":1778635172653},\"metadata\":{\"openai\":{\"itemId\":\"msg_0287e6321648d158016a03d1a049388198a1e9cdd342ee175e\",\"phase\":\"commentary\"}}}}\n{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1778635172671,\"sessionID\":\"ses_1e11580c0ffeSwchj8aKCTzhE6\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"grep\",\"callID\":\"c