{"type":"text","timestamp":1778624742055,"sessionID":"ses_1e1b5c3bfffeDl9SPU25UAOtSU","part":{"id":"prt_e1e4bbf2d001Hu8IMH4hzi1jvN","messageID":"msg_e1e4af41f0013bRigmk8IJqayq","sessionID":"ses_1e1b5c3bfffeDl9SPU25UAOtSU","type":"text","text":"I’ll write the hypothesis around a register-file structural retime: replace the wide resettable FF array with a scrubbed LUTRAM-style regfile so CoreMark sees identical initialized state while FPGA area and reset fanout drop.","time":{"start":1778624741165,"end":1778624742054},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_069fe7d70fea59be016a03a8e507b48194bee5825bd3e4b7e2","phase":"commentary"}}}}
