{"type":"text","timestamp":1778635204230,"sessionID":"ses_1e11580c0ffeSwchj8aKCTzhE6","part":{"id":"prt_e1eeb642f001BbGiByYkRlzAhR","messageID":"msg_e1eeaecc9001T1wtStdg5G0DI0","sessionID":"ses_1e11580c0ffeSwchj8aKCTzhE6","type":"text","text":"I’m writing a single-file predictor hypothesis: selectively keep low-cost JAL prediction for loop-like/direct jumps while dropping forward call JAL prediction, to reduce IF target-cone cost without losing the backward-branch win.","time":{"start":1778635203631,"end":1778635204230},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0fd27a6df70a4112016a03d1c349088198a211bcdbfd9305a9","phase":"commentary"}}}}
