{"type":"text","timestamp":1778624654335,"sessionID":"ses_1e1b5c423ffeJqKIDO72eUxe5w","part":{"id":"prt_e1e4a673d001mwKvueO6WOomTi","messageID":"msg_e1e4a58890011FoGWLFeKyjJ44","sessionID":"ses_1e1b5c423ffeJqKIDO72eUxe5w","type":"text","text":"Prior predictor history shows the only strong win was the current stateless JAL plus backward-branch fetch predictor; BHT, RAS, and funct3 refinements all lost to added IF-path cost. I’m writing a lower-cost predictor hypothesis that avoids new dynamic state and instead specializes the existing static predictor for CoreMark’s direct unconditional control flow.","time":{"start":1778624653117,"end":1778624654333},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_02330f38007634b9016a03a88d06548193b1517cc8214c82dd","phase":"commentary"}}}}
