{"type":"text","timestamp":1778627266900,"sessionID":"ses_1e18e1a3affejfQrNsUBf0JFiO","part":{"id":"prt_e1e724735001Qe0yu7aEPa3qQg","messageID":"msg_e1e72072d001txzt4wBpy5ZTnQ","sessionID":"ses_1e18e1a3affejfQrNsUBf0JFiO","type":"text","text":"Prior predictor attempts show the only clear win was the stateless JAL/backward-branch predictor; broader dynamic state, indirect prediction, and loop-exit learning all regressed from IF-path cost. I’m going to keep the hypothesis in the predictor category but target the predictor’s timing cost rather than adding more prediction state.","time":{"start":1778627266357,"end":1778627266898},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0de2747b950dd901016a03b2c241b481939392d6740f2c2607","phase":"commentary"}}}}
